span.span: Due to extended mandated shelter in place, MAPS #124 buildings will continue to be closed but remote learning and student engagement will continue. As per Governor Pritzker's April 17th announcement, in person learning is suspended for the rest of the 2019-2020 school year.

h1.span: The District will continue meal service for students. There are two ways you can sign up for meal service: One, by filling out the google form sign up sheet to the right of this home page. Secondly, you can call either the HS office at 815-889-4184, or the GS office at 815-889-4174 and leave a voice mail.

br.span: Pickup will be on Mondays from 9:30 a.m. to 10:30 a.m. at the Milford HS office lobby and the Sheldon School main entrance. Students will be given 5 breakfasts and lunches on Monday. We will no longer be doing pickup on Thursdays until further notice.
